S-Track electric actuators are designed for better control and quieter operation in general duty applications including medical, industrial, turf & garden and recreational vehicles. This S1 model has a gear ratio of 11: 1, 24 VDC standard motor, and a load capacity of 175 lb (778 N). The S-Track series has stroke lengths ranging from 4 to 12 in (100 to 300 mm), with this specific unit having a 6 in (150 mm) stroke length. This unit allows for keypad adjusted control, with the main benefit being able to change the end limit stop locations and two additional stops if needed.

K2vL units are weatherproofed with Nitrotec corrosion protection and high performance powder coat paint.
